            <thetext>Simulator applications (generated using e.g. simulation-build in a skeleton app) no longer run since they include Sinon (qx.dev.unit.MMock) which tries to access window.location, causing an exception on startup. This dependency was introduced with recent changes to testrunner.runner.TestRunnerBasic (bug #5788), which is used by the Simulator.

We should move these dependencies to testrunner.runner.TestRunner.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
